      "Replication": "Disabled",
      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "data;\n\n// check any invalid elements\ninvalidList = data[2];\nisEmpty = List.IsEmpty(invalidList);\nerrorMessage = \"Error! Please view Checking Schedule ^_^\";\n\n// if invalid list contains value, (isEmpty == false) terminate script\n// else statement as terminus\nallowData = [Imperative]{\nif (isEmpty == true) // change this bool for testing\n\treturn [data[0], List.Empty, List.Empty];\nelse\n\treturn [List.Empty, data[2], errorMessage];\n};\n\n\"Warning!\";\nallowMessage = allowData[2];\n\n//output\nvalidElements = allowData[0];\ninvalidElements = allowData[1];"
    },
