      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "data;\navailableNames;\n\n// get elements with nulls\nelementsWithNulls = data[2];\n\n// check element counts\nisEmpty = List.IsEmpty(elementsWithNulls);\nallowData = [Imperative]{\nif (isEmpty == false)\n\treturn elementsWithNulls;\nelse\n\treturn List.Empty;\n};\n\n// get element system names\nsystemNames = Revit.Elements.Element.GetParameterValueByName(allowData, \"System Name\");\nsplitNames = DSCore.String.Split(systemNames, [\",\"]);\n\n//output\nelementsWithNulls;\nsplitNames;\navailableNames;"
    },
