      "Replication": "Disabled",
      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "views;\n\nsetViewPurpose = Revit.Elements.Element.SetParameterByName(views, \"View Purpose\", \"99 - Report\");\nsetViewPackage = Revit.Elements.Element.SetParameterByName(views, \"Package\", \"Report - Mechanical\");\nsetViewSubPackage = Revit.Elements.Element.SetParameterByName(views, \"Sub-Package\", \"Error Schedules\");"
